    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お金がほしいわ……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか、いきなり……\nでも、ないですね。いつもお金の話ばかりしてますし",
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね、人を金の亡者みたいに\n年末は何かと出費がかさむので、ただの愚痴です",
      "startTime": 17.5666669846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ新曲出ますし、クリスマスにはライブもありますし\n仕事があれば、ギャラも入るからいいんですけど",
      "startTime": 26.2000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ年末は、テレビの収録スケジュールやら何やら\n前倒しになって、きついったら",
      "startTime": 32.83333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "厳しい日程でお願いしてしまって、すみません……",
      "startTime": 35.5000017167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "まー、kanaは仕事ぎちぎちの中でも\n楽しそうにクリスマス配信の仕込みをしてますし",
      "startTime": 42.03333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "私も正直、浮かれたカップル眺めてたって\n鬱陶しいだけですから",
      "startTime": 48.9666683834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoだけはこの時期になると\nいつにも増して辛気くさいですけど",
      "startTime": 53.2666711808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、忙しいうちが華とはいえ\nちょっとくらい、年末らしいこともしたいですねぇ",
      "startTime": 59.3000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "年末らしいもの……年末……うーん\nああ、年末の宝くじなんてのもありましたっけ",
      "startTime": 69.7000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ\n確かに、そんなものもありましたねぇ",
      "startTime": 77.9333327612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "う～、寒っ\n芸能人って普通、タクシーとか車で移動しますよね",
      "startTime": 86.2000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "なんでうちだけ毎度、電車なんですか\nかき入れ時にアイドルが風邪引いたらどうするんです",
      "startTime": 93.5666706722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "け、経費削減にご協力下さい……",
      "startTime": 97.0666706722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんにちゃんと言っといて下さいよ\n……そういえば、あそこに見える宝くじ売り場",
      "startTime": 105.1333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "あそこの売り場\n何度も高額当選者が出てるんで、有名らしいですよ",
      "startTime": 110.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "ま、ただの確率の問題だと思いますけどね\n店員が笑顔の売り場で買うと当たるなんて言いますけど",
      "startTime": 118.5333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "結局、愛想がいい所で買う人が多いから\n母数が多い分、当選者数も増えるってだけのことですし",
      "startTime": 126.2333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……\nfranさんも、宝くじ買ったりするんですか？",
      "startTime": 132.3333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "あんな運任せのものに手を出したりしませんよ\nどうせ当たる確率なんて、二千万分の一なんですから",
      "startTime": 138.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "……日本だと一等前後賞でもせいぜい数億円ですけど\n海外だと六百億が出たこともあるらしいですね",
      "startTime": 148.6000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば、知ってます？\n宝くじって、江戸時代の初期頃からあるらしいですよ",
      "startTime": 154.5000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから、宝くじの話しかしてませんけど……\nつまり、気になってるんですね？",
      "startTime": 161.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつも株やってるじゃないですか\nその延長線上と思えば、別に買ってもいいのでは？",
      "startTime": 166.8333403906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "株をギャンブルみたいに言わないで下さい\nあれはれっきとした経済学です",
      "startTime": 174.0333403906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "かのニュートンだって、株やってたんですから\n……まぁ最後は四億くらい損したらしいですけど……",
      "startTime": 180.2000070573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに四億はどうかと思いますけど、数枚くらいなら\nほら、年末のちょっとしたお楽しみってことで",
      "startTime": 188.2999928158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、無駄遣い出来るお金はあんまりないし……\nうーん……",
      "startTime": 196.4333292009,
